    <item>
      <title>花旗银行的 Montagu 表示，科技股面临巨大抛售风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tech-stocks-at-significant-risk-of-selloff-citi-s-montagu-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团策略师表示，尽管美国科技股过去一个月遭遇抛售，但投资者的看涨仓位仍然保持，因此该股面临“巨大压力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tech-stocks-at-significant-risk-of-selloff-citi-s-montagu-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 11:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员称中东紧张局势不会推动油价“大幅”上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-13/oil-won-t-rise-materially-on-middle-east-tensions-sen-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Energy Aspects 创始人兼研究主管 Amrita Sen 在讨论中东地缘政治紧张局势对市场的潜在影响时表示：“我们预计这些不断升级的紧张局势不会造成直接的供应损失。” Sen 还研究了如果 OPEC+ 继续实施下个季度增加供应的计划，全球石油库存将如何变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-13/oil-won-t-rise-materially-on-middle-east-tensions-sen-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 11:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pandora 首席执行官表示，十年后，合成钻石将比天然钻石更受欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pandora-ceo-says-diamond-market-faces-disruption-in-next-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pandora A/S 的首席执行官预计，用不了 10 年，消费者购买的实验室培育钻石就会多于天然钻石，因为他们在购买珠宝时越来越多地考虑成本和气候影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pandora-ceo-says-diamond-market-faces-disruption-in-next-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谈判破裂后，必和必拓顶级铜矿工人开始罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/bhp-workers-at-biggest-copper-mine-to-strike-after-talks-fail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团位于智利的埃斯孔迪达铜矿的工人因未能达成工资协议将于周二开始罢工，这为这家全球最大铜矿的停产埋下了伏笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/bhp-workers-at-biggest-copper-mine-to-strike-after-talks-fail</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
